INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (731,1,'2014-06-13 16:52:30','2014-06-13 16:52:30','<h2 class=\"widgettitle\">ROS Spotlight: Shadow Robot&rsquo;s <img\r\nsrc=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/RoNeX_logo_small.png\"/></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This ROS Spotlight introduces Shadow Robot&rsquo;s new platform for\r\nconnecting ROS to robot hardware.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A spin-off <a\r\nhref=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stiff-flop.eu%2Fimages%2Fnewsletter%2FD6.3.2_Newsletter.pdf&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNGGtze156FkF36KXGwsmhZ-42wHlg\">from\r\nthe Stiff-Flop Project</a>, RoNeX is designed specially for cutting\r\nedge robotics prototyping and development. RoNeX provides a high\r\nspeed, modular I/O network that fully integrates with ROS straight out\r\nof the box, accessible directly on ROS topics or within standard ROS\r\ncontrollers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Utilising the industrial strenght real-time EtherCAT field-bus,\r\nRoNeX has 100Mbps of bandwidth available, and maintains a 1 kHz update\r\nrate on all channels allowing for real time joint control from a ROS\r\nHost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To show just how easy it is to build a robot with RoNeX, Shadow has\r\ndone just that in this video:</p>\r\n<center> <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\"\r\nsrc=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Dk5-1W1d6zw\" frameborder=\"0\"\r\nallowfullscreen></iframe> </center>\r\n<p> Using standard ROS packages for joint control, kinematics, path\r\nplanning and visualisation, Shadow needed only ten new lines of code\r\nplus a URDF file automatically generated from Solidworks to drive the\r\nrobot!</p>\r\n<p>The Shadow team is releasing RoNeX with three Modules available now\r\nand are putting the final touches to a roadmap that includes motor\r\ndrivers, ability to daisy chain RoNeX stacks and Dev Kits for advanced\r\nusers and OEMs.</p>\r\n<p>To find out more about RoNeX visit the <a\r\nhref=\"http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shadowrobot.com%2Fproducts%2Fronex&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNEp1UUcB80oa3HyLBrQp1lWeLr70w\">Shadow\r\nWebsite</a>.</p>\r\n<p>RoNeX drivers are <a\r\nhref=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fshadow-robot%2Fsr-ronex&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNHRP60nL22OyAh5xPqPAceAdcUPlw\">open\r\nsource on Github</a> and the user manual <a\r\nhref=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fshadow-robot%2Fsr-ronex%2Fwiki&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNGbniZLP1g4vVHdBf_8v0NBTdM1zg\">is\r\nhere</a>.</p>\r\n<hr class=\"horizontal-separator\">\r\n<p>If you\'d like us to spotlight your project here, send us a note at\r\ninfo AT osrfoundation DOT org.\r\n<br><a href=\"http://www.ros.org/news/spotlight/\"\r\ntarget=\"_blank\">Previous spotlights</a></p>','ROS Spotlight','','inherit','closed','closed','','268-revision-v1','','','2014-06-13 16:52:30','2014-06-13 16:52:30','',268,'http://www.ros.org/268-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
